#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_mesh/mesh.rst:322
msgid ""
"For 2D/3D meshes, select the :guilabel:`Resampling method` to interpolate"
" the values on the surrounding vertices to the faces (or from the "
"surrounding faces to the vertices) using the :guilabel:`Neighbour "
"average` method. Depending on whether the dataset is defined on the "
"vertices (respectively on the faces), QGIS defaults this setting to "
":guilabel:`None` (respectively :guilabel:`Neighbour average`) method in "
"order to use values on vertices and keep the default rendering smooth."
msgstr ""

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_mesh/mesh.rst:328
