#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_mesh/mesh.rst:413
msgid ""
"**Length**: Specifies the length of the wind barbs. Choose the units from"
" a drop-down menu."
msgstr ""

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_mesh/mesh.rst:415
msgid ""
"**Data Units**: Specifies the units of wind speed data. Wind barbs encode"
" the wind in knots (nautical miles per hour). Therefore, you should "
"select the units that your data are in, or use a custom "
":guilabel:`Multiplier` to convert your data units to knots. This ensures "
"that the wind speed is accurately represented."
msgstr ""

